text: Hugo Magnetti (born 30 May 1998) is a French professional footballer who plays as a midfielder for French club Stade Brestois 29 in the Ligue 1. ==Professional career== Born in Marseille, Magnetti spent his youth career with various local clubs in his hometown before moving to SC Bastia in Corsica at 16. On 31 May 2018, Magnetti joined Stade Brestois 29 in the French Ligue 2. Magnetti made his professional debut with Brest in a 1–0 Ligue 2 loss to FC Metz on 30 July 2018. ==References== ==External links== * * Category:1998 births Category:Living people Category:Sportspeople from Marseille Category:Association football midfielders Category:French footballers Category:Stade Brestois 29 players Category:SC Bastia players Category:Ligue 1 players Category:Ligue 2 players Category:Championnat National 2 players
